'''Amar Memić''' ({{IPA|bs|ǎmar měmitɕ|pron}}; born 20 January 2001) is a Bosnian professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Midfielder#Winger|winger]] for [[Czech First League]] club [[FC Viktoria Plzeň|Viktoria Plzeň]] and the [[Bosnia and Herzegovina national football team|Bosnia and Herzegovina national team]].

Memić started his professional career at [[FK Radnik Hadžići|Radnik Hadžići]], before joining [[NK Bravo|Bravo]] in 2021. The following year, he moved to [[MFK Karviná|Karviná]]. In 2025, he signed with Viktoria Plzeň.

A former youth international for Bosnia and Herzegovina, Memić made his senior international debut in 2025, earning 13 [[Cap (sport)|caps]] since.

==Club career==

===Early career===
Memić came through the youth setup of [[FK Radnik Hadžići|Radnik Hadžići]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://reprezentacija.ba/450667-novo-zanimljivo-ime-za-barbareza-sarajlija-u-timu-polusezone-u-ceskoj-vec-je-igrao-za-mlade-selekcije-bih|title=Novo zanimljivo ime za Barbareza: Sarajlija u timu polusezone u Češkoj, već je igrao za mlade selekcije BiH|website=reprezentacija.ba|date=22 December 2024|access-date=22 December 2024|language=bs}}</ref> He made his professional debut against [[NK Travnik|Travnik]] on 8 August 2020 at the age of 19.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://sportsport.ba/fudbal/torlak-junak-travnika-podjela-bodova-u-zivinicama/371233|title=Torlak junak Travnika, podjela bodova u Živinicama|website=sportsport.ba|date=8 August 2020|access-date=11 August 2020|language=bs}}</ref> On 6 September, he scored his first professional goal in a triumph over [[FK Igman Konjic|Igman Konjic]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://sportsport.ba/fudbal/vladavic-i-memic-vodili-radnik-do-rutinske-pobjede/374485|title=Vladavić i Memić vodili Radnik do rutinske pobjede|website=sportsport.ba|date=6 September 2020|access-date=9 September 2020|language=bs}}</ref>

In July 2021, he signed with Slovenian club [[NK Bravo|Bravo]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://sportsport.ba/fudbal/sjajan-transfer-iz-prve-lige-fbih-dosadasnji-fudbaler-radnika-otisao-u-sloveniju/403314|title=Sjajan transfer iz Prve lige FBiH: Dosadašnji fudbaler Radnika otišao u Sloveniju|website=sportsport.ba|date=10 July 2021|access-date=11 July 2021|language=bs}}</ref>

In August 2022, he joined Czech team [[MFK Karviná|Karviná]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://sportsport.ba/fudbal/memic-pronasao-novi-klub-pricao-sam-sa-sehicem-odluka-mi-je-odmah-bila-laksa/432188|title=Memić pronašao novi klub: Pričao sam sa Šehićem, odluka mi je odmah bila lakša|website=sportsport.ba|date=19 August 2022|access-date=22 August 2022|language=bs}}</ref>

In January 2025, Memić was transferred to [[FC Viktoria Plzeň|Viktoria Plzeň]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://scsport.ba/amar-memic-potpisao-trogodisnji-ugovor-s-viktorijom-plzen|title=Amar Memić potpisao trogodišnji ugovor s Viktorijom Plzeň|website=scsport.ba|date=27 December 2024|access-date=30 December 2024|language=bs}}</ref>

==International career==
Memić was a member of the [[Bosnia and Herzegovina national under-21 football team|Bosnia and Herzegovina under-21 team]] for several years.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://klix.ba/sport/nogomet/memic-nevjerovatan-je-osjecaj-naci-se-na-spisku-selektora-i-biti-ovdje-s-reprezentativcima/250318167|title=Memić: Nevjerovatan je osjećaj naći se na spisku selektora i biti ovdje s reprezentativcima|website=klix.ba|date=18 March 2025|access-date=21 March 2025|language=bs}}</ref>

In March 2025, he received his first senior call up, for [[2026 FIFA World Cup qualification – UEFA Group H|2026 FIFA World Cup qualifiers]] against [[Romania national football team|Romania]] and [[Cyprus national football team|Cyprus]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://radiosarajevo.ba/sport/nogomet/barbarez-odabrao-igrace-za-utakmice-s-rumunijom-i-kiprom-jedno-novo-ime-na-spisku/580816|title=Barbarez odabrao igrače za utakmice s Rumunijom i Kiprom: Jedno novo ime na spisku|website=radiosarajevo.ba|date=3 March 2025|access-date=3 March 2025|language=bs}}</ref> He debuted against the former on 21 March.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://avaz.ba/sport/nogomet/962742/pocetak-kvalifikacija-kao-iz-snova-zmajevi-srusili-rumuniju-usred-bukuresta|title=Početak kvalifikacija kao iz snova: Zmajevi srušili Rumuniju usred Bukurešta|website=avaz.ba|date=21 March 2025|access-date=23 March 2025|language=bs}}</ref>

On 12 October, in a [[Exhibition game#Association football|friendly]] game against [[Malta national football team|Malta]], he scored his first senior international goal.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://oslobodjenje.ba/sport/fudbal/reprezentacija/foto-cetiri-razlicita-strijelca-za-pobjedu-protiv-malte-zmajevi-odlicni-u-prijateljskoj-utakmici-1082635|title=Četiri različita strijelca za pobjedu protiv Malte: Zmajevi odlični u prijateljskoj utakmici|website=oslobodjenje.ba|date=12 October 2025|access-date=12 October 2025|language=bs}}</ref>

In June 2026, Memić was named in Bosnia and Herzegovina's squad for the [[2026 FIFA World Cup]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://sportske.ba/clanak/barbarez-poslao-konacan-spisak-fifa-i-jedno-ime-otputovalo-u-ameriku-ali-nije-na-listi|title=Barbarez poslao konačan spisak FIFA-i: Jedno ime otputovalo u Ameriku, ali nije na listi|website=sportske.ba|date=3 June 2026|access-date=3 June 2026|language=bs}}</ref>

